title: SWAT Simulation for Las Vegas from 2001 to 2010
author: Venkatesh Merwade
abstract: This is a SWAT model instance that includes all the input and processed GIS data, and input/output model data for SWAT. The model is crated and calibrated for Las Vegas by using climate data from 2001 to 2010.

Las Vegas
